extends baseEmail

block content
    p Hi,
    p You are receiving this because you (or someone else) have requested the reset of the password of your account 🎉🙏
    p please click on the following link, or paste this into your browser to complete the process within 10 minutes of receiving it.
    table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
        tbody
            tr
                td(align='left')
                    table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
                        tbody
                            tr
                                td
                                    a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Reset Your Password
    p If you did not request this, please ignore this email and your password will remain unchanged.😀
    a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') #{url}
    p - Boss Dater